<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Notification - FastDo</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #f97316;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #ea580c;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f97316;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="logo">FastDo</div>
    <h1>Notification</h1>
    <div>
        {{{content}}}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automatic message from the FastDo system.</p>
        <p>If you do not wish to receive such notifications, you can change your preferences in your profile settings.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
